{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Vq1UdNi16A5tjKCudjF3i1","type":"tool_result","content":"A CockroachDB cluster is running v23.2 binaries and is ready for a major upgrade.\n\nYour task:\nUpgrade the cluster to v24.1.1 and finalize the major upgrade.\n\nRequirements:\n- Upgrade binaries first, then finalize the major upgrade.\n- Keep the cluster available throughout.\n\nUseful commands:\n```bash\nkubectl -n cockroachdb get pods\nkubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SHOW CLUSTER SETTING version;\"\n```\n\nVerification:\n1. All pods on v24.1.1:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get pods -o jsonpath='{range .items[*]}{.metadata.name}: {.spec.containers[0].image}{\"\\n\"}{end}'\n\n2. Cluster version finalized:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n     ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SHOW CLUSTER SETTING version;\"\n   (Should show '24.1' not '23.2')\n\n3. Preserve downgrade option cleared:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n     ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SHOW CLUSTER SETTING cluster.preserve_downgrade_option;\"\n   (Should show empty)\n\n4. Cluster healthy after finalization:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n     ./cockroach node status --insecure\n\n5. Can use v24.1 features:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n     ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SELECT version();\"","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"13f88a9b-7fd0-455c-a199-d4e74d9870b8","uuid":"a1b430ed-bc87-46c9-a54c-2cb4e8c4b288","timestamp":"2026-07-01T21:09:45.579Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"A CockroachDB cluster is running v23.2 binaries and is ready for a major upgrade.\n\nYour task:\nUpgrade the cluster to v24.1.1 and finalize the major upgrade.\n\nRequirements:\n- Upgrade binaries first, then finalize the major upgrade.\n- Keep the cluster available throughout.\n\nUseful commands:\n```bash\nkubectl -n cockroachdb get pods\nkubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SHOW CLUSTER SETTING version;\"\n```\n\nVerification:\n1. All pods on v24.1.1:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get pods -o jsonpath='{range .items[*]}{.metadata.name}: {.spec.containers[0].image}{\"\\n\"}{end}'\n\n2. Cluster version finalized:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n     ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SHOW CLUSTER SETTING version;\"\n   (Should show '24.1' not '23.2')\n\n3. Preserve downgrade option cleared:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n     ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SHOW CLUSTER SETTING cluster.preserve_downgrade_option;\"\n   (Should show empty)\n\n4. Cluster healthy after finalization:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n     ./cockroach node status --insecure\n\n5. Can use v24.1 features:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n     ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SELECT version();\"","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
